    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "> Or adding yet another hack of translating keccak256(...code) in the codegen? I would rather not.\r\n\r\nActually a good point against this is the push for code merkleization (i.e. [EIP-2926](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-2926)) which would change the way the codehash is calculated.",
